<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Account Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #000000;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .body {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #555;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #333333;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <img src="https://openfxt.vercel.app/images/favicon.png" alt="Logo" class="logo" />
                <h2>Account Verification</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <p>Hello <b><%= username %></b>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering your account on <b><a href="<%= appUrl %>" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none;"><%= appName %></a></b>. To complete the registration process, please verify your account by clicking the link below:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" class="btn">Verify Account</a>
            </div>
            <p>This link will expire in 24 hours. If you did not request this, please ignore this email or contact us if you have any questions.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>Reseter</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent automatically, please do not reply.</p>
            <p>If you need assistance, contact us at <a href="mailto:nguyenhuutai@reseter.space">nguyenhuutai@reseter.space</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
